籤詩版本二:
Mitengo ya mitengo ya paini ndi ya mkuyu ikuphuka bwino, ndipo mvula, chipale chofewa, mphepo, ndi chisanu ndizo zonse zofunika kuchita.
Tsogolo lidzagwiritsidwa ntchito modzidzimutsa, ndipo kutchuka kudzakhala mzati.
詩意:
Hexagram iyi ili ngati nkhalango yobiriwira ya mitengo yapaini ndi cypresses.
Muli olemekezeka m'chilichonse.
解曰: Zabwino zonse panjira. Utumiki wabwino wa moyo wonse. Mbozi zam'munda zapsa. Banja likuyenda bwino.
籤詩故事一:
◇Fan Wenzheng adaganiza zokhala ndi phala
Fan Zhongyan, mkulu wodziwika bwino mu ufumu wa Song, anachokera kubanja losauka ali wamng'ono. Anaphunzira kunyumba ya amonke ku Changbai Mountain. m’zigawo zinayi ndi mpeni.
Izi zimagwiritsidwa ntchito pofotokoza munthu amene saopa zovuta, amaphunzira mwakhama, ndipo pamapeto pake amakhala talente yogwiritsa ntchito kwambiri.
Dulani phala ndikujambula phala
聖意: Jiazhai amadzifunira yekha, kufunafuna chuma, mtendere, bizinesi, ukwati, kupambana, Liujia, oyenda pansi amuna, malo okhulupilira, mphutsi za silika, ziweto zisanu ndi chimodzi, zowonongeka, kufufuza anthu, milandu, kusamuka, kutaya katundu, matenda, Anshan manda, auspiciousness.
古人: Fan Wenzheng aganiza zobowola ndi kujambula phala
